  "name": "RPlog_The_Third_Battle_of_Coruscant_Part_I",
  "title": "Storming the Coruscant Palace",
  "summary": "The Imperial offensive for Coruscant reaches its climax as a massive assault descends on the Plaza before the Palace, where half the New Republic Senate and the President shelter. New Republic troops under officers like Brain, Skeezix, and the senator-protector Jandis dig in with tanks and artillery as AT-AT walkers, dropships, and screaming stormtrooper columns led by Kizuka and Darkholme converge from every street and balcony. Amid the carnage, the wanderer Simon hunts the crowd for his lost companion Mira, who flees the firestorm into the Palace, while the Sith huntress Kacela stalks Simon through the slaughter, sensing his presence. Their lightstaff-and-lightsaber duel becomes the heart of the chapter, Simon reliving childhood terror of the fallen Selas as Kacela drives him back and even hurls a dying soldier at him, forcing Simon to cut the man down. As Imperial grenadiers blast a hole in the Rebel line, speeder cavalry pour through, and the Palace gate is breached, the New Republic forces fall back toward the Palace to protect the senators and clear an evacuation path.",
